::Feline::

She woke up and walked out of the CR chamber.  She had a long scare 
on her side.  The spots now looked miss matched along her side where 
the scare was.  She frowned, then walked out of the lab.  She 
transformed into leopard mode and ran out of the entrance of the 
base. She opened her link. "Zardus, where are you? Still fighting? 
I'll be there." She ran hard to join her comrads in arms.
